Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's the one who stole my bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you come down to the station with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:17.80,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(289,304)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Masquerade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:21.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop my heart from dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:30.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Crying and laughing, we never forget our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:41.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Finding your true self
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And becoming an adult is difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I can forget for now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The night is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:55.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As our hearts beat excitedly in rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:57.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And we frolic about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:01.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nearly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we are afraid of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You cannot move if you remain empty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:18.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right if we have fun, so let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:22.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I forget all my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and dance the night away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:32.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become someone more wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:36.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This endless Golden Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The distance between us as you approach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:42.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neither closes nor widens
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:46.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll treasure this even it it's the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:53.37,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(287,54)}Traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:53.37,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(282,84)}Division
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:54.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait here until your parents arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll be off the hook with just some paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:12.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've inconvenienced you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, I thought you still hadn't forgotten about Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were so shocked when he confessed to Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:30.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wasn't shocked that Mitsuo confessed to Miss Ultrasonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was sad for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:36.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:41.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Miss Ultrasonic easily acquires what I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:44.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A fun life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,New friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:55.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought she was going to get you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It made me sad to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:06.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Accepting that I was more and more attracted to you was really difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:13.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I was just attracted to your kindness because of the pain of being rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:17.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was suspicious of my own motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:25.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's why, according to my plan, the correct answer was no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:31.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To mature on my own and be the one to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:36.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought it was the right thing to do, and I believed it would change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Things don't go according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'd make us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It would not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga Kouko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your father is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm Kouko's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I intend to go apologize to the owner of the bicycle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I couldn't inconvenience you any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My daughter is stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I hope this won't stop you from being her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:17.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:20.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What a crazy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.91,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(157,146)}{\i1}Incoming Message{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.91,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(188,211)}{\i1}Linda-senpai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.91,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(181,267)}{\i1}No subject{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.91,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(117,328)}{\i1}I want to talk to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.91,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(113,358)}{\i1}Call me back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ro-me-o-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your Juliet has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning, my boyfriend Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You waited for 30 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, so I could say "good morning" to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You could've texted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to express my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:29.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A poor dog who died waiting for her owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like Hachiko, the Faithful Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We really do understand each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aw... but I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I had waited for you in front of your place,\NI could have been with you longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You don't need to wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We can just meet somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That won't do at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:04.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want to waste a single second or meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,From your first step and second of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:25.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just glad we're dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, Tada-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll meet you at your place every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not easy for me to say this, but you can't come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are your parents opposed to us dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They can't be! I'm harmless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:45.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They think I'm harmful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:49.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Harmful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:54.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My father said I should stay away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He said that if a weird girl like me clings to you, it'll ruin your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He asked if you were my new target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Was Yana-san your old target?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Our future looks grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:14.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like Romeo and Juliet, we might poison each other eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... they didn't poison each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:17.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why?! When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.65,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(297,412)}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Man, you're too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I... I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Pro wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:48.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san, you look so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I was kind of hating myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so I went to get my head shaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:05.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The person at the store asked to practice on my head if I was going to cut it off anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:07.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, what's up with Banri and Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aren't you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:19.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was surprised for a second, but I'm not shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I kind of figured they'd end up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As far as I could tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you're an unusually tolerant guy who could handle dating Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,For me, it's a load off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I've finally been freed from the evil spirit that's been clinging to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:46.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You sound like you must have recovered completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After Miss Ultrasonic rejected you so pitifully, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Saying in her cute little ultrasonic voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"What? Are you stupid?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I would've been like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:58.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,OM...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,OMG!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're a strong boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,K-Kaga-san, we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't want to leave you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wish we were taking the same classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's stay together during breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's eat lunch together, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's stay together after school, too-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just go! You're an eyesore for singles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's "OMG"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, My Guts are failing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Osha-Mambe Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't believe what I said at the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have you seen Oka-chan since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But if I do, I intend to interact with her normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I CAN'T DO IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:07.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was just going to say that I'm free first period today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He didn't need to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If he keeps acting like that, I don't know what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:22.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't count what happened the other day as a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It happened at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But if he runs away from me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:28.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Several days passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san and I went to and from classes together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and remained together at college.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sometimes we even went on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:58.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai texted me nearly every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...but I never replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you finish cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll make myself at home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:33.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:43.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just vegetables my parents sent over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't we sit over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have brought some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I found a store by the station with nice-looking sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the Bamboo Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, how do you know what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need to understand you better, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bet you have potatoes in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's something else I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:34.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you asking about Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said so yourself the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I asked if something happened with Linda-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you said the answer was "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:46.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:51.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If it's difficult for you to tell me,\NI wasn't planning on asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I'm curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Things were awkward between you and me that day, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:02.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai was worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I guess I lashed out at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Things are awkward between us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll make up with her eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does that explain things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:16.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, are these potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I-it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's normal to be interested in these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,W-well, I am a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But we've only just started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We should let it happen naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...in Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:05.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The first time we're in that situation together,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,it's going to be in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:18.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll spend that fateful night in Paris, the city of lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go buy a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How are we getting to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:31.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We can buy plane tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's buy them! I want to buy them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The Eiffel Tower awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Eiffel, my Eiffel Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Eiffel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When are we practicing with the festival club next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... next Friday, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She seemed kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.08,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(300,264)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}New Message
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.08,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(304,293)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Linda-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.83,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(427,83)}No
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.83,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(399,115)}smoking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, magical girls are in right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A text?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}New Message\NLinda-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, isn't your phone ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:56.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't recognize the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The realtor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The room next to yours has a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Could you make sure your room hasn't flooded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll head right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's a leak at my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've got class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:25.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll text you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:26.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You ignored me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We met in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you not notice we're neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:51.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:56.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I went to greet you a few times after I moved in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but you never answered the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought that was just how Tokyo people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm originally from Warabi in Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Warabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:10.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...is yours the room that flooded?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm the one who called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I-it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai forced me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't know you lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:20.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If there's something you want to say, spit it out and get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stand it when you're being indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:28.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My shoes are still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Would you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She used to be in the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:49.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After I joined, she became busy with her band and work, and she quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She kept hanging out with me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does Nana-san go to our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's a third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Also, her real name isn't Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:05.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I told her things were awkward between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,she told me Tada Banri lived next door to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's how...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So this is your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is where you live, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:49.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I only confused you more, doing things halfhearted like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:52.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:02.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to meet you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was willing to give up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I prayed to God to let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:20.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're alive. You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't ask for anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:30.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:35.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't know what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see... So this is how you found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was our relationship like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:58.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In high school, we were really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were funny and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you were kind of unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even though we're the same age,\NI was like your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Things aren't any different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:23.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, the other day you said it was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:25.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We were close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That much is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:37.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but you said you wanted to be with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You confessed your feelings to me on the night of our graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:45.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The next day, I was supposed to give you my answer on that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then I was on that bridge because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought, if I had been on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:02.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...maybe you wouldn't have fallen from the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've caused you a lot of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:13.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I just want to support you as your senior,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:15.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and as someone who knows about your accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why would you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Because you're Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if you don't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:30.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you're important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:34.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I enjoy spending time with you, Tada Banri.
